Upstream EF Core SQLite attribution
================================================================================

Substantial portions of this provider will be derived from the Microsoft
Entity Framework Core SQLite provider (`Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Sqlite`
/ `src/EFCore.Sqlite.Core` in the EF Core repository), which is licensed under
the MIT License:

  Copyright (c) .NET Foundation and Contributors
  https://github.com/dotnet/efcore

When the upstream import commit lands, this section will record:

  - Upstream repository: https://github.com/dotnet/efcore
  - Exact tag and commit SHA
  - Published EF Core package patch (currently targeting 10.0.10 — see docs/versions.md)
  - Imported source paths under this repository
  - Import date

Microsoft-authored baseline files retain their original copyright headers.
Community modifications for libSQL / Nelknet.LibSQL.Data remain in separate
commits so the customization delta stays reviewable.

